title: Ask HN: Is there already an HN Discord?
text:
I'm thinking of creating one on an invite-only basis (at least to start).

Does an HN oriented Discord already exist?

Would you be interested in joining?

Some of y'all really inspire me, mikkergp, bombcar, sn0w_crash, PaulHoule, chatterhead, and other /new friends. I'd love to have a channel of our own.

Ask HN: How to I optimize a warm intro to a well known figure?
text: I have a close connection who is willing to introduce me to a well known figure. I'd like to meet this person because I believe they would be a good seed investor for an idea I have. I think the idea is strong (but it's just an idea). I'm curious what other factors I should consider when reaching out. Thanks!
